# Demo image builds from the repo root. keep the context lean.
**/node_modules
**/.next
**/.turbo
**/dist
**/build
.git
.github

# python / worker (not part of the demo image)
**/.venv
**/__pycache__
**/.pytest_cache
**/.ruff_cache

# local state + secrets
**/*.sqlite*
**/*.db*
**/.env
**/.env.*
!**/.env.example

# not needed in any image build context
infra
test-results
playwright-report
**/_local
**/_scratch
